title: DPS BestOf
itunes:title: DPS BestOf
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's play-in games. Did the T-Wolves go over the top with the celebration? Mike Florio calls in to summarize the Washington Commanders latest scandal. And Chris Haynes shares some details about a conversation that he recently had with Grizzlies guard Ja Morant.
